{
  "stem": "3659.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that really helped the child very much [LAUGHS] growing up, but that was the way it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember one very funny incidence, just came to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in third year in high school, and I've got very bad midterm grades, and I really didn't know how to tell my father.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to get the signature on his-- on, you know, to-- on the diploma, and I didn't know how to go about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I sort of inched up to him and I says, papa, the most important thing is I'm healthy, and I handed him my report card.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he couldn't get angry at me because the way I explained it to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's funny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just thought about it, thinking about school and, you know, doing this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as I said, schooling was uppermost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Learning was uppermost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I love to sew, and I love to do embroideries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I have embroidery here at home, which I'll be happy to show you-- petit point and crocheting and knitting, which really came in very handy later on in my life.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always enjoyed doing that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I also liked history, because it piqued my interest and to know how other people, you know, how they live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And history was very important, and to this day, I enjoy it very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And basically, as I said, my sister also studied Japanese, because she was supposed to go to Japan for the Olympic Games as her graduation present.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father felt if you go to that country or any country, you better speak the language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He did not believe that you should not speak languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he spoke about three or four languages himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
